author: Lenard Monkman
title: Couple shaves their eyebrows as motivation to stay home during COVID-19 pandemic
description: Justin Young and Justine Manuel in Kamloops, B.C., shaved off their eyebrows as extra incentive to stay home and avoid socializing.
content:
It started with a meme.
Justin Young and Justine Manuel were sitting at home in Kamloops, B.C., when they saw a meme that said "if you are having a hard time staying home, shave off your eyebrows."
